kopete (4:4.14.1-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Team upload.
  * Remove (apparently unused) libgnutls-dev build dependency.
    (Closes: #764102)
  * Update copyright.
  * Change from googletalk-call to libjingle-call in the kfreebsd .install
    exclusion.
  * Update .install files.
  * Add an explicit kdelibs5-dev build dependency before kdepimlibs5-dev;
    this should help pulling phonon-backend-dummy as build dependency instead
    of a real backend, even if some library depends on phonon.

 -- Pino Toscano <pino@debian.org>  Sun, 05 Oct 2014 17:33:19 +0200

